<section class="doc-section">
  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <div class="doc-code"><button class="doc-copy">copy</button><pre>&lt;div class="q2w-draw q2w-draw--floating"&gt;
  &lt;button class="q2w-draw__btn is-active" title="Point"&gt;...&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;button class="q2w-draw__btn" title="Line"&gt;...&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;button class="q2w-draw__btn" title="Polygon"&gt;...&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;span class="q2w-draw__sep"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;button class="q2w-draw__btn"&gt;Edit&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;button class="q2w-draw__btn"&gt;Delete&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre></div>
</section>

<section class="doc-section">
  <h2>Behavior</h2>
  <p>Use this component as a visual shell around Leaflet Draw or a custom editing workflow. The preview simulates active-tool switching so the UI state is visible during documentation review.</p>
</section>

